info.title: Installed Base
info.description:
Installed base is a hierarchical arrangement of items installed at your customerâ€™s location.

Use this API to do the following:
- View the list of maintained installed bases.
- Get information about customer, contact, location, and status, and access an installed base.
- Create new installed bases. Disclaimer: The list of entity type collections displayed under API References is not complete. To view the comprehensive list, see the service metadata.
